</p>
<p>Yes!</p>
<p>Finally, in <code>bootstrap.php</code>, instead of manually checking for <em>just</em> this one class,
say that the path is always equal to <code>__DIR__/lib/</code> then <code>str_replace()</code> - we'll
replace the back slash with a forward slash:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="8a16755026">
